Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:27.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  快点啦
