Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  要去散步了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.77,0:00:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:00:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在咕哝什么呢  唯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  和和
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.14,0:01:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在为选什么志愿学校而烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  志愿调查表还没有交吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家早就交了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是但是  我脑袋又不灵光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.93,0:01:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大学的事情也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.75,0:01:18.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…唯  这样下去真的会变成NEET啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.75,0:01:18.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Not in Employment, Education or Training）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次说这话很沉重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就做NEET算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「NEET」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和最后第一志愿填了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:20.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？  我填了国立学校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然感觉有点鲁莽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我想以那个目标努力冲刺一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也填那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太轻率了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为与和和在一起比较好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在闹什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  唯她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  你还没决定志愿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪填了什么第一志愿？
