Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  你知道推荐是什么意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:03:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:03:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,填了什么
