Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也填那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我适可而止吧
