Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.41,0:04:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认清现实了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.02,0:04:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是日本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要英语！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:33.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们仅靠日语就能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校的英语考试不及格是会留级的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是入学考试的话  只要在别的学科上取得好成绩就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  语文也有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古文
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  传给小律
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:05:00.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请选择和下面的助动词用法相同的一项
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西没学过～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是一年级的范围哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助动词可以通过歌来记住  以前没学过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:18.89,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（以「龟与兔」曲调的助动词记忆歌，歌词为记忆大意）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.97,0:05:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:24.14,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痒痒的麻疹真想要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:31.48,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田园摩摩摩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:34.32,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跌啊踢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:36.38,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:41.30,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小羊贝西真是认真
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:46.33,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这么吵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:24.14,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,む ず む ず じ し む まし まほし～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:31.48,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,る ら ら る さーす りー りー りー
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:34.32,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,つ ぬ たり け り たし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:36.38,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,た し き けむ～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:41.30,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,らむ べし らし まじ なーり めりー
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:46.33,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうしてそんなり たり ごとし～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:30.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（现在开始比赛跑）（好  来比）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（在半途中休息）（趁现在）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:36.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（怎么了）（其实是被欺负了）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:39.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我来带你去龙宫城）（那真是太感谢你了）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:41.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（千年）（万年）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是记得很清楚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这个该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就完全没意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律填了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:05:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我写了未定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还完全不清楚将来的出路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.91,0:06:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那我也写未定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭一张纸可决定不了我们的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.13,0:06:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:17.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年二班的田井中同学和平泽同学  马上到办公室来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:18.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…果然不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  你们先去活动室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦啊  和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪也是  彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯从小时候开始就完全没变过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说已经进步不少了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律也是  认真干的话是能干好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯也是  集中力很强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个话题  到活动室里继续说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会如此兴奋呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.13,0:06:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:07:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才广播里叫的是唯学姐她们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  总之是她们自作自受而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又干了什么错事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…就是有点关于将来出路的问题要商谈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  请用  和和
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  和是什么时候认识唯的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从幼儿园开始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么样的邂逅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…没什么特别的契机…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.60,0:07:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不知不觉中就在我身边了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是本能地感觉到你是个可靠的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  你已经画好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能舔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就是那样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  从那时开始就经常在同一个班级
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定有着不可思议的缘分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多伤脑筋的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说伤脑筋的话可能确实伤脑筋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学时  我们去野营
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没听说要带方便食品吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像唯学姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来  还有在家政课上做章鱼烧的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,材料是由大家带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  把章鱼拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责章鱼的唯忘了带章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.64,0:09:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果做了无章鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使没有章鱼也很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无章鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别的还有很多说都说不完的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一看到那无邪的笑容  就不知为何会原谅她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就那样了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  刚才说过唯也已经进步不少了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得那大概是多亏了轻音部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和真像大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  感觉像妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…母…母亲！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的将来要好好考虑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯还没决定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:10:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得还远着呢  太难想象了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很远的事了  一转眼就到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和也上了年纪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来小佐和在高中时明明是那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:14.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会想成为老师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  为什么为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.71,0:10:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  很难为情…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想作参考  请一定要告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是因为当时喜欢的人说想成为老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就说「那我也要做老师」…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动机不纯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢  和那个人怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但托了那个人的福才会进入大学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为了老师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  重要的不是过去  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是现在啊  小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  现在也没有男朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  唯  怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:11:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又知道了一件小佐和过去的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  没有被骂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～感觉人生真是各种各样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不会又搞出了什么事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是  我是说人经历了各种事情之后就会变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.69,0:11:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  志愿调查表那样行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么将来想做的职业吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的职业吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  你觉得什么比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己决定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学的时候不是说过想做幼儿园的老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得是在发表题目为「将来的梦想」的作文的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将来的梦想是成为幼儿园的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想成为幼儿园的老师之后  和小朋友们一直玩下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像唯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到发表作文  澪有一次获得了优秀奖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  别说那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想听  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想听
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓  我们来练习吧  练…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就放弃吧  澪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.86,0:12:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学时候的澪是个很文静很老实的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得一直都在看书
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是乎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:13:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时比现在还要害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  给我看看  给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个反应很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪画画也很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我经常逗她玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  100分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  我也想逗她玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是欺负吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:17.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:21.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学的时候不是会去逗自己喜欢的人玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那种
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是刚开始关系并不是特别好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的啊  被那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到这些事情之后就觉得焦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.03,0:13:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把额头伸过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:35.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的额头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是水性笔  放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  作文的发表怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还…还记得？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.27,0:13:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么吧  澪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说给大家听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是三眼星人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.95,0:13:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小学四年级的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的作文获得了县级奖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得奖的人要在全校集会时在大家的面前朗读
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不想朗读而沮丧着的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律来找我分担烦恼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  不想读作文  为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很害羞啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好害羞的啊  你可厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一点也不厉害啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可班里就澪一个人得奖啊  要是我的话就向大家炫耀了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小律去得奖不就行了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想在大家面前读啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:15:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪居然也能这么大声说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.11,0:15:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得…好有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.24,0:15:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  现在去我家吧  来特训！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别磨磨蹭蹭的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.77,0:15:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来  有请四年一班学号1号的秋山澪同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.22,0:15:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读不出来啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:23.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  台子低了点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再垫高点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:27.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是这个问题啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:30.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:32.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个拿下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这样子  这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  扎好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菠萝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲告诉我  紧张的时候就把观众全部当作马铃薯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不会扮马铃薯  就扮个菠萝～菠萝给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:16:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不像啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.95,0:16:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…此后在人与人之间广为流传
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完  四年一班  秋山澪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.63,0:16:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏律  让我放松了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这故事真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律学姐之前是个好孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那果然不像小律该当的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不知道怎么诚心赞扬别人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  那作文发表进行的顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…澪写的作文啦  内容很童话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痒痒痒痒痒…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请谅解这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过自那之后就经常去律家里玩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  我教了你很多东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要改掉害羞的性格就要对自己自信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:17:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是说话的方式  句末里加个「哦」的话就看起来自信满满了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:03.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是秋山澪  哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  就是这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…还真是很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一想感觉你真没教什么正经的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.58,0:17:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不应该找律帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好过分啊  小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.07,0:17:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯不是也这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.32,0:17:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不过还是要感谢她把我带上音乐这条路…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪\N小澪\N澪学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我说  现在不是听我和律的故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于你们两个的志愿调查要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  总之先别想复杂的  大致考虑下自己想做什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那么开个花店怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个听上去不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫平泽唯  是镇上的花店老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种花难养吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:01.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（倒闭）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…这需要植物相关的知识啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  做个公司里的OL怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是新人OL  今天也要迟到了  哎嘿～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的公司在隔壁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.18,0:18:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打…打扰了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…要守时很困难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵你好过分…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公交导游说不定不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  可以免费去各处旅游
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.62,0:18:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.39,0:18:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是大家的公交导游
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大家请看你们的右手边  右手边…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在右手边有…唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.41,0:18:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…容易晕车的人做不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  服务生怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个服务生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得记好多客人的菜单哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点心师呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是点心师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉会被自己吃掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就写上自己现在最想做的怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己最想做的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:21.68,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}第一希望　音乐家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.69,0:19:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驳回
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明认真去写了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.18,0:19:35.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告队长  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音乐家…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我认真点写！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:41.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是很认真的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是太惊讶了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这是为了让和和笑起来而进行的笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:19:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不  她觉得这是天方夜谭哦  唯同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧毕业了准备干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不出口…担心姐姐  想和她去同一个地方这种话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我还没有想过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  得好好想想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你呢  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.59,0:20:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…还没想好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想做个美容师  准备去考美容师的专业学校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.14,0:21:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去艺术大学吧  我想学摄影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有摄影这门课吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去外国语大学  然后去中国留学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去护士学校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回家里的酒坊帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越来越不知道写什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.01,0:21:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:36.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}第一希望　总之\N第二希望　会努力\N第三希望　加油的\N{\fs18}　　　　　　{\s1}护士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.25,0:21:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驳回
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.83,0:21:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.64,0:21:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.28,0:23:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…小佐和你怎么了
